{"tid":1369132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［最後的勸諫］聽日有晒劇本，但香港人一定要企出黎！","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:58:53.000Z","uid":85622,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6aeef93f1b23d44cd2acb93d11e0e46ff1c5ed","tid":1369132,"uid":85622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"過左咁多次行動，勇武、和理非大家都知道要點做，識得互相尊重，合作補位，目標一致。亦因為咁，所有行動一直都取得到成果。<br />\n<br />\n但係各位，而家唔係話我地無做就無做，假若<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有人有心嫁媧</span></span></strong>，有人收左錢做嘢，老屈示威者，到時水洗都唔清。<br />\n<br />\n所以聽日每個行動都要清晰，盡量唔好挑起爭執、引起混亂，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">比有心人乘機趁火打劫</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n請謹記，聽日行出黎嘅目的只有一個，就係要話畀政權知，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">任何事情都不會令到我地有所畏懼！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n僅只如此！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">萬一有事，請盡快拉走你身邊所有人，離開現場，切勿陷入三幫人嘅大亂戰。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1c4716ff0ed1717c75d8946e1cbe1b6fcbf90d76","tid":1369132,"uid":199834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"點都好 放火真係不可取"},{"pid":"b93af7f781696f53fa6cc02089655422f4d2e48d","tid":1369132,"uid":85622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:10:01.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"97d3217d71ee3e50ed45a09987f6ae5dc2048cf8","tid":1369132,"uid":85622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"3afb39685441fadefcefdd40b5b3b3e77362594f","tid":1369132,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山, 做乜都好, 搵咗攻略睇先! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再on 99 講有事退去寫字樓! </span></span><br />\n元朗有L寫字樓/商場你退!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a